Package bsiopis.webapp.controller

Class UserInput

java.lang.Object
bsiopis.webapp.controller.UserInput
public class UserInput extends Object
User Input Class. The UserInput class works as a Data Transfer Object (DTO) in order to effectively pass values inside the address fields of the User class
